{"tid":1744934,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，覺醒！《都市傳說－蜥蜴人》","createTime":"2019-11-22T03:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T09:01:39.000Z","uid":116322,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d6764b0b33f7586c4f24d41ca61aead856144b9a","tid":1744934,"uid":116322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VhO5zw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVhO5zw7.jpg&h=3fec1336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相傳，外星人早已入侵並悄悄統治地球幾千年。這外星物種被稱為蜥蜴人 (Reptilian)，真實面貌極為醜陋，以人類為食糧。<br />\n<br />\n之所以沒被人類發現，是因為蜥蜴人能變形為人類的樣子，生活在人群裡，甚至成為「菁英」或政府高官控制人類。<br />\n<br />\n蜥蜴人視人類比牠們低等、人類是牠們的奴隸、人類的生命根本不值一提。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYWF7R7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYWF7R7.jpg&h=835c1188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了全面控制社會，蜥蜴人派出低級行動部隊，屠殺所有勇敢反抗的人類、清洗異見族群，每天明刀明槍地犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n諷刺的是，竟有一班人類作為幫兇去殺害同類。<br />\n有些為蜥蜴人拍掌；有些歌頌蜥蜴人不殺之恩；<br />\n有些則安然活在大型屠宰場裡，讚嘆蜥蜴人丟出來的豬餿美味又便宜。<br />\n<br />\n荒誕都市，荒誕的人與事。<br />\n<br />\n身為人類，無論站在蜥蜴人、人類或「中立」一方，要不等著被宰殺，要不將蜥蜴人逐出地球，別無他選。為甚麼？這牽涉到蜥蜴人的 Agenda。<br />\n<br />\n蜥蜴人的終極目標，是創立新世界秩序 (The New World Order)。One World, One Government。牠們認為只有牠們這高貴種族才配享用地球資源，而地球上近 90%的人口則是多餘，這跟光明會的人類大清洗滅絕計劃很類近，亦有人相信，光明會的管理層擁有蜥蜴人血統。<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，你以為舉著旗號大聲高呼支持蜥蜴人，最終能逃過一死嗎？<br />\n<br />\n還有那些生活在平行時空的「中立」人類，你認為所有敢於發聲的人類被清洗後，下一個不會輪到你嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人類，覺醒吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關於陰謀論啊甚麼的，我不曉得自己能寫多久，你們的like和share能給我勇氣，讓我繼續寫下去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hGMriYP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhGMriYP.jpg&h=8463c449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n請Follow<br />\n👇Facebook: 橘子綠茶👇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/greenizmstory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgreenizmstory&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=b049317f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/greenizmstory</a><br />\n<br />\n👇Instagram: greenizmstory👇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/greenizmstory/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgreenizmstory%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=31c5463a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/greenizmstory/</a>"},{"pid":"97585f6ba4e1baf1376357b2787ca1fc688a0060","tid":1744934,"uid":169482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76b475d2321b510c3fdbf446715e1198fd4542b","tid":1744934,"uid":249097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:47:19.000Z","msg":"留個名先"},{"pid":"93f9466dbd8866710477aee684671a26b10b3e01","tid":1744934,"uid":116815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b33825fdf31abc73fa0f11d1fb7c13dc08a217","tid":1744934,"uid":204629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:56:12.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c8b62a59c7209d57ba6ba90a3093ff96090d281e","tid":1744934,"uid":116818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"Lm"}]}